News for Version 1.3
  
  * added 'RESCOREFACTOR' environment variable for setting the rescoring
    factor during runtime

News for Version 1.2

  * added 'set_log_Limmat' option to enable logging after initialization

News for Version 1.1
  
  * configure script
  * 64 bit port to Alpha under Linux
  * added compile time options to enable/disable various optimizations
  * skip arguments to '-t' and '-n' for multiple CNF files in main.c
  * fixed broken max decision bound in limmat.c
